data.description: This mid-century ranch is ready for new memories with a new family. The seller has made tons of updates and serious repairs. The next family will certainly have peace of mind. The property been redone throughout and offers tons of living space up and down with unique features. The garage was converted years ago into a huge living space equipped with a fireplace to give you precious family memories and quality time together Just in time for the winter months. All brick exterior with newer Windows, and a newer roof less than 3 years old complete with new decking, new furnace and AC in 2020. The basement has a great second living space and a another bedroom as well as a 4th non-conforming bedroom with a very comfortable jacuzzi tub. The back yard is massive and an absolute dream for anyone with the time and creativity. The yard is also equipped with a garage pad ready for a new garage to be built to your liking. This property is priced with the buyer in mind and situated in a convenient location. This home won't last long, and Buyers are securing properties right now. Call your realtor today for the next buyer appointment. All information obtained from Seller and public records. Seller has a full radon report and majority of the receipts for work he has done. A separate list of repairs and work done on hand.  submit your offer today. Seller will look at all reasonable offers. Radon report will be provided at the time of accepted offer. HOME SOLD IN "AS IS" CONDITION
